item.title: Help!
item.dc:creator: @mopar_I mopar I
item.description:
@mopar_I wrote:

Answer To Q1: Open up Moparscape, and go to “help” on the top. Then go to the last 3 things on the list that is on there. Search something that you would want to spawn. For example an item:

::pickup [item ID] [ammount],or, ::item [item ID] (Note: the item appears below you when you do ::item.

Answer to Q2: Go to the RS2 Server Advertisment Section,

moparisthebest.com

moparisthebest.com

programming, irc, cars

Find a server that fits your needs.

Some server s require something called hamachi,get it here.

https://secure.logmein.com/products/hamachi/download.asp

For any further information, feel free to PM me.
